{"id": 1671, "genre": 1001, "title": "最佳雇主评了那么多，你觉得什么才是真正的职场关怀？", "description": "没有座金光闪闪的最佳雇主奖杯傍身，500 强简直都不好意思自称大公司。", "record_count": 3487, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170505221637GwENFXeiJbRr9Dpd.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-06T17:00:02Z", "options": [{"id": 201472, "content": "别强行灌鸡汤，企业文化不等同于洗脑，和而不同尊重每个人的三观才是正道", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939567}, {"id": 201986, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/201705090808433A2b4zdkJ6ZpRxjP.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027056}, {"id": 201475, "content": "工作就是能够全身心的投入。不会因为公司的其他事而影响。对睡都不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668830}, {"id": 201479, "content": "不闲着没事就是坐班", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793857}, {"id": 201480, "content": "记油啊", "image": "img/option/option/20170507183153i1gL7zl8ksUVqpEQ.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818819}, {"id": 201481, "content": "少开没必要的会。好用的电脑。符合人体工学的舒服的办公椅。畅通快速的网络。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 375024}, {"id": 201738, "content": "啊哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232590}, {"id": 201483, "content": "加班 年终奖金都要一视同仁", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000221}, {"id": 201486, "content": "有固定的办公时间，不无故加班。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602900}, {"id": 201488, "content": "加薪", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 202517, "content": "发钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996732}, {"id": 201494, "content": "想贝兼的➕V信 2227887341，曰结", "image": "img/option/option/20170507201236IDPr67YMTB0sFunE.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025733}, {"id": 201751, "content": "心不累，钱到位。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026474}, {"id": 201500, "content": "每个人都为了做成同样一件伟大的事情而努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339969}, {"id": 201502, "content": "弹性工作制，让你知道你的工作是有意义的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404762}, {"id": 201503, "content": "不要让我一直打电话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010872}, {"id": 201506, "content": "人文关怀以及企业文化，每个部门要有自己的凝聚力\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975122}, {"id": 204835, "content": "追求安稳的人有一个萝卜一个坑做十年的环境，也有给鸡血族一条上升通道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034694}, {"id": 201509, "content": "疑人不用，用人不疑", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933599}, {"id": 201510, "content": "别让单身的女孩子9点以后还要回办公室加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819794}, {"id": 215846, "content": "有明确的升职空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062759}, {"id": 201511, "content": "公平公正公开！这个绝不能就套路了！凡是面试女性的时候问打不打算生孩子的统统都没资格做什么最佳雇主", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 201512, "content": "满足碎觉前的好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025771}, {"id": 201514, "content": "提供饮用水就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262145}, {"id": 201515, "content": "给够买房的工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955981}, {"id": 214571, "content": "不是涨工资吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059432}, {"id": 201518, "content": "情怀和收入两者皆有", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025814}, {"id": 206126, "content": "愿意花钱和时间培养员工", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467350}, {"id": 201519, "content": "待遇合理，不玩剥削就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024456}, {"id": 207407, "content": "辞退整天游手好闲还拿一样工资的人，把钱给真正干活的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1035412}, {"id": 201776, "content": "明确的晋升空间！让人有一个奋斗的目标！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026525}, {"id": 201009, "content": "桌椅符合人体力学", "image": null, "praise_count": 134, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 202033, "content": "基层服务行业的工作人员遇到野蛮无理客人的时候领导也能挺身而出在后面撑腰", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948844}, {"id": 201010, "content": "有舒适的午休空间", "image": null, "praise_count": 95, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 201522, "content": "足够休息。足够薪水", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 207410, "content": "有良好的工作环境，工作氛围，最好是年底公司带我们出去环游世界。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015448}, {"id": 201012, "content": "有明确公开的升职加薪路径", "image": null, "praise_count": 621, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 201524, "content": "能学到东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025847}, {"id": 202037, "content": "关注员工的职场发展目标，关键时刻push员工坚持下去。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027278}, {"id": 201526, "content": "公开公正的评价机制 让员工有工作动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025875}, {"id": 201529, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793310}, {"id": 203577, "content": "关怀体现在实事而不是口号上。曾经雇主也拿了个什么最佳，但其实很多人都工作得怨声载道，这种评比结果就见仁见智吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031407}, {"id": 201530, "content": "阶层少一些，拍板的少一些，内耗少一些。工资多一些，假期多一些，配套福利多一些。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864759}, {"id": 201531, "content": "转正加薪！别忽悠！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979400}, {"id": 206140, "content": "说白了就是钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036176}, {"id": 201792, "content": "情怀和投入", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 233024}, {"id": 201538, "content": "HR少点套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246132}, {"id": 201794, "content": "跟我说能者多劳的同时，给钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429463}, {"id": 201796, "content": "不要团建，不要为了活跃气氛开会，不要强迫人参加拓展活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506536}, {"id": 201541, "content": "把人当人而不是只把管理层当人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1025935}]}